  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Hola! I am Viktorija, a volunteer Field Traveler for GlobalGiving. During March-September 2019 I am visiting nonprofit partners in South America (Chile, Colombia, Ecuador and Peru). During 6 months in the field my role is to strengthen connections with existing nonprofit partners through project site visits. Apart from that, I am also leading workshops about efficient fundraising, facilitating peer discussions on vital topics and providing a platform to learn from and share success stories.</narrative>
  </description>
